Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.25,0:00:02.41,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Are there different kinds of milk as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.88,0:00:09.58,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,That’s right; although they’re basically all the same, depending on how they’re prepared there are different kinds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:11.25,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Different kinds?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.45,0:00:13.12,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Yes, just like in tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.37,0:00:18.02,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Depending on which leaves are picked and how they're prepared, the same leaves can be very different.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:19.86,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,People, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:20.33,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:22.66,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Are there different kinds of people as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:29.96,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Hmm, well, rather than kinds, each person is different in his or her own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:35.96,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,For example, you don’t like tea, but there are also people like me who love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:41.08,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,There are also people whose stomach gets upset when they drink milk, but there also those who don't have that happen to them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.09,0:00:47.34,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,However, there also people who learn to drink it when they grow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.30,0:00:52.93,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Lain, you’ll probably learn to drink tea, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.56,0:00:56.69,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,It’s not a good thing, nor a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:01:02.50,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,It’s normal that there are different kinds of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:06.13,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,That's why you can be proud of what makes you unique!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:07.65,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,Be proud of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:15.21,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I’m sorry... That’s right, you worry, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.61,0:01:21.90,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You don’t have to boast about it, but there’s no need to mind what other people think, is what I meant to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:26.42,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I have weird dreams. Is that different, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.02,0:01:31.94,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You may think it's different, but in fact that’s normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:38.10,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If you’re worried about that, I might be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:45.48,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Not to help you stop having those dreams, but rather helping you to explain things you don’t understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:48.61,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If you come to me with your problems, I’d be really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:55.50,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You know, I’ve studied a lot to help you answer those kinds of questions; I’m still studying, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:02:05.19,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If you’re ever in trouble or something, I'd be glad if you could come and talk with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:11.06,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I’d like to know more about you, Lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:13.30,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Would that be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:17.40,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I’m so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:20.41,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Starting today, you and I are friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:22.00,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Please come and play sometime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:22.82,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:26.65,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,I’d like to ask you things as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:28.78,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,You can ask me anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:31.34,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,If I don’t know the answer, I’ll look up the answer for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:35.32,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,I’ll even prepare your favorite drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:36.57,Default,Lain,0,0,0,,What’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:40.34,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Milk that doesn’t upset your stomach!
